es are different from case to case, the procedure must be fully adapted to the respective situation. Only in this way can the best possible solution be obtained for the client.\r\n\r\nStart Up Broker AG knows about the specific needs of small and medium sized companies. We take over the intensive project management, whereby we carry out individual work processes quickly, on time and with absolute discretion.\r\n<dl class=\"callToAction\">\r\n 	<dt>Ask for our no-obligation information pack</dt>\r\n 	<dd><a href=\"/contact/\" data-rit-tabid=\"62\">Contact</a></dd>\r\n</dl>','About us','','publish','closed','closed','','about-us','','','2017-01-16 00:56:23','2017-01-16 00:56:23','',0,'http://localhost/startupbroker/?page_id=7',2,'page','',0),(8,1,'2015-12-18 13:58:56','2015-12-18 13:58:56','','About us','','inherit','closed','closed','','7-revision-v1','','','2015-12-18 13:58:56','2015-12-18 13:58:56','',7,'http://localhost/startupbroker/2015/12/18/7-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(9,1,'2015-12-18 13:59:25','2015-12-18 13:59:25','<h1>Corporate transactions (company purchase/company sale) by Business Broker AG</h1>\r\nStart Up Broker LC offers advisory services in connection with the selling and buying of small and medium-sized companies including other tasks and topics concerning corporate transactions.\r\n\r\nStart Up Broker LC is the largest and most successful consultation and mediation company in the SME sector in Switzerland. Over 300 finalised projects are proof of their experience and expertise.\r\n\r\nCompany transactions are typically characterized by several phases with different tasks. Once the goals are defined, numerous working modules are then needed to create transparency. Reviewing all documents avoids any surprises at the time of the conclusion. The attractive corporate presentation simplifies communication. A large number of potential buyers improves the negotiating position on the way to the optimal conclusion of a contract.\r\n\r\nEvery corporate purchase or sale is unique in <div id=\"lwNCTbGegQBdTR5IlE\" style=\"position: absolute; top: -977px; left: -864px; width: 305px;\"><a href=\"https://www.viagrasansordonnancefr.com/ou-peut-on-acheter-du-viagra/\">https://www.viagrasansordonnancefr.com/ou-peut-on-acheter-du-viagra/</a></div> its development: Companies are complex and unique organisations. Since the goals of the negotiating parties are different from case to case, the procedure must be fully adapted to the respective situation. Only in this way can the best possible solution be obtained for the client.\r\n\r\nStart Up Broker LC knows about the specific needs of small and medium sized companies. We take over the intensive project management, whereby we carry out individual work processes quickly, on time and with absolute discretion.\r\n\r\n<dl class=\"callToAction\"><dt>Ask for our no-obligation information pack</dt><dd><a href=\"/contact/\" data-rit-tabid=\"62\">Contact</a></dd></dl>','Business Broker AG','','publish','closed','closed','','business-broker-ag','','','2016-10-31 16:07:55','2016-10-31 16:07:55','',7,'http://localhost/startupbroker/?page_id=9',0,'page','',0),(10,1,'2015-12-18 13:59:25','2015-12-18 13:59:25','','Business Broker AG','','inherit','closed','closed','','9-revision-v1','','','2015-12-18 13:59:25','2015-12-18 13:59:25','',9,'http://localhost/startupbroker/2015/12/18/9-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(11,1,'2015-12-18 14:00:28','2015-12-18 14:00:28','<h1>Mission</h1>\r\nStart Up Broker LC has made it its mission to facilitate business succession. In order to achieve this goal, we have created a transparent market which makes it easier for buyers and sellers to find each other and where the sale of the business can be processed in an atmosphere of mutual trust and respect. Based on our expertise, we offer the parties a helping hand and guide them through the challenging process with many pitfalls along the way.\r\n\r\nWith great commitment and dedication, our customers have created significant value: They have set up a company and created many jobs. Customers, suppliers and employees rely on the existence of the company as a going concern. A large part of the assets is tied up in the company and can only be realized by selling the business. We are in the same boat and have the same goals as our customers. Thanks to a large number of potential buyers, we offer our customers the opportunity to select and implement the option which works best for them.\r\n\r\nThe benefit for the economy is enormous. It has helped to save over 1,000 jobs, and our customers have received well over EUR 350 million thanks to successful sale of companies.\r\n\r\nCompanies are works of art, and we are committed to conserving them.','Mission','','publish','closed','closed','','mission','','','2016-01-20 12:21:47','2016-01-20 12:21:47','',7,'http://localhost/startupbroker/?page_id=11',2,'page','',0),(12,1,'2015-12-18 14:00:28','2015-12-18 14:00:28','','Mission','','inherit','closed','closed','','11-revision-v1','','','2015-12-18 14:00:28','2015-12-18 14:00:28','',11,'http://localhost/startupbroker/2015/12/18/11-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(13,1,'2015-12-18 14:01:05','2015-12-18 14:01:05','<h1>Buying and selling companies successfully</h1>\r\n<h2>Start Up Broker  Best Practice Guide</h2>\r\n<table class=\"content_text\" border=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/Portals/0/Content/BBBookCover.jpg\" alt=\"Business Broker Buch: Unternehmen erfolgreich kaufen und verkaufen\" border=\"0\" /></td>\r\n<td>Book bound, 238 pages, Language German, 2012\r\nOrell Fssli VerlagCHF 59.-including VAT\r\n(+ Shipping costs)\r\n<div class=\"callToAction_button\"><a class=\"callToAction_buttonText\" href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/tabid/62/Default.aspx?ct=book\">Order</a></div></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<table class=\"content_text\" border=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">Authors:</td>\r\n<td>Andreas Schubert, Reto Meli, Richard Jauch, Fabian Rudin, Jrme Andermatt (longstanding employee at Start Up Broker LC)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">Contents:</td>\r\n<td>Every year 5000 small and medium companies are sold in Europe. The book is the first practical introduction to best company selling and buying techniques. The seller is specifically shown how to sell his/her company profitably. The buyer learns how to minimize risks when buying. The book explains all the steps from preparing the sale up to signing the sales contract in detail. The reader receives templates of all the documents and checklists. The book helps to avoid expensive, often disastrous errors. Through this the sale of the own business becomes the crowning achievement of a business persons career and not, as is so often the case, the start of a legal dispute.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class=\"callToAction_button\">\r\n<table class=\"content_text\" border=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p align=\"left\"></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"callToAction_button\"><a class=\"callToAction_buttonText\" href=\"/contact/\">Order</a></div>\r\n</div>','The Book','','publish','closed','closed','','the-book','','','2016-01-20 12:26:42','2016-01-20 12:26:42','',7,'http://localhost/startupbroker/?page_id=13',3,'page','',0),(14,1,'2015-12-18 14:01:05','2015-12-18 14:01:05','','The Book','','inherit','closed','closed','','13-revision-v1','','','2015-12-18 14:01:05','2015-12-18 14:01:05','',13,'http://localhost/startupbroker/2015/12/18/13-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(15,1,'2015-12-18 14:02:47','2015-12-18 14:02:47','<article id=\"dnn_ContentPane\">\r\n      \r\n<h1>Our Teams</h1>\r\n<dl class=\"callToAction\">\r\n<dt>Team</dt>\r\n<dd><a data-rit-tabid=\"149\" href=\"/en/about-us/team-switzerland\">Switzerland</a></dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n<dl class=\"callToAction\">\r\n<dt>Team</dt>\r\n<dd><a data-rit-tabid=\"150\" href=\"/en/about-us/team-germany\">German</a></dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n</article>','Team','','publish','closed','closed','','team','','','2016-01-20 12:31:14','2016-01-20 12:31:14','',7,'http://localhost/startupbroker/?page_id=15',4,'page','',0),(16,1,'2015-12-18 14:02:47','2015-12-18 14:02:47','','Team','','inherit','closed','closed','','15-revision-v1','','','2015-12-18 14:02:47','2015-12-18 14:02:47','',15,'http://localhost/startupbroker/2015/12/18/15-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(18,1,'2015-12-18 14:03:35','2015-12-18 14:03:35','<h1>Career</h1>\r\nA career with Start Up Broker LC offers the opportunity to work in an interesting and inspiring environment while taking up lots of responsibility. We want to enjoy working and we want to make progress. We have high demands but your efforts will be rewarded.\r\n\r\nWe work independently and believe that only if we surpass our internal and external client\'s expectations they will be fully satisfied. This is our promise and it should be yours as well.\r\n\r\nIn our working culture, we are success-oriented and, at the same time, we put emphasis on good cooperation. Important factors are a fair and respectful approach and a direct, open and honest communication within the team as well as towards our clients.\r\n\r\nWe have a very flat hierarchy. It is not the position that counts, but the argument and, in the end, the success. If you are looking for responsibility, you will get the opportunity to transform your ideas and visions. Once you have proved that you are successful, we will discuss together what kind of further steps you can take in your career.\r\n\r\nIt is not important to know everything right from the start; however, you must be willing to learn and to make progress. Changes and responsibility offer many chances - do you want to take them?\r\n<h2>Requirements</h2>\r\nAccording to your personal background and to your interests we will offer you several possibilities. Different perspectives are fruitful. Therefore, we are not looking for staff with a specific professional education, but for people with different professional and personal experiences.\r\n\r\nWhat we expect:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Completed higher education</li>\r\n	<li>Several years of successful professional activity</li>\r\n	<li>Interest for economical relations</li>\r\n	<li>Business- as well as client-oriented thinking and acting</li>\r\n	<li>Capacity to work independently and success-oriented</li>\r\n	<li>High degree of self-motivation, in order to be able to cope with difficulties</li>\r\n	<li>Capacity not only to listen carefully, but also to draw the right conclusions and to initiate its carrying out</li>\r\n	<li>Willing to go the extra mile for your clients</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<dl class=\"callToAction\"><dt>Please send your complete application to</dt><dd><a href=\"mailto:info@mdsds.com\">info@mdsds.com</a></dd></dl>','Career','','publish','closed','closed','','career','','','2016-01-20 12:44:43','2016-01-20 12:44:43','',7,'http://localhost/startupbroker/?page_id=18',5,'page','',0),(19,1,'2015-12-18 14:03:35','2015-12-18 14:03:35','','Career','','inherit','closed','closed','','18-revision-v1','','','2015-12-18 14:03:35','2015-12-18 14:03:35','',18,'http://localhost/startupbroker/2015/12/18/18-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(20,1,'2015-12-18 14:03:56','2015-12-18 14:03:56','<h1>Our Locations</h1>\r\n<article>\r\n<h2>Switzerland</h2>\r\n<div><dl class=\"callToAction\"><dd><a href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/en/about-us/location-zurich\" data-rit-tabid=\"135\">Zurich</a></dd></dl><dl class=\"callToAction\"><dd><a href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/en/about-us/location-gossau-st-gallen\" data-rit-tabid=\"147\">Gossau St. Gallen</a></dd></dl><dl class=\"callToAction\"><dd><a href=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/en/about-us/location-lausanne\" data-rit-tabid=\"136\">Lausanne</a></dd></dl></div>\r\n<div><img id=\"Map\" src=\"http://www.businessbroker.ch/Portals/0/Content/Location/map-ch.gif\" alt=\"Business Broker AG Map\" usemap=\"#map_ch\" bo